msgctxt "Npc_Musician_015_003"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah, so the \"<2.se_co>wings of cloth and wood<3.re_co>\"\n"
"referred to a paraglider. Of course.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>The way you soared on the wind made it\n"
"look as though you truly had wings.<5.ra><6.so>I feel the stirrings of a "
"new song about\n"
"your deeds here...\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>Take care, and may the light illuminate\n"
"your path."
msgstr ""

