msgctxt "Npc_Musician_015_R_006"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The \"tempestuous bay\" from the song\n"
"could be this very bay.<2.pa> But what sort of\n"
"wings are made of cloth and wood?\n"
"<3.so>It's a juicy riddle, but one I may never\n"
"puzzle out.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Take care, and may the light\n"
"illuminate your path."
msgstr ""

